WEBVTT

00:01.130 --> 00:03.394
PREVIOUSLY
ON "VERONICA MARS"...

00:03.430 --> 00:04.795
I SEE
THE PROZAC'S WORKING.

00:04.830 --> 00:07.298
I'VE GOT A SECRET --
A GOOD ONE.

00:08.470 --> 00:11.132
SOCIALLY, SHE SEEMS TO BE
A BIT ISOLATED.

00:11.170 --> 00:13.536
I'D SAY VERONICA'S DOING WELL
GIVEN THE CIRCUMSTANCES.

00:13.580 --> 00:15.434
I KNOW HOW CLOSE
SHE WAS WITH LILLY KANE.

00:15.480 --> 00:17.209
THE TRUTH IS GONNA COME OUT.
IT DOESN'T ADD UP.

00:17.250 --> 00:18.444
LILLY?

00:18.480 --> 00:20.619
WHAT, YOU FORGOT
ABOUT ME ALREADY?

00:20.650 --> 00:22.117
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

00:22.150 --> 00:23.481
WHY DO YOU HAVE
LILLY'S NAME ON YOUR ARM?

00:23.520 --> 00:25.340
YOU REALLY WANT
TO KNOW?
YEAH!

00:25.390 --> 00:28.154
MY HUSBAND GETS A LOT
OF DISTURBING LETTERS FROM FANS.

00:28.190 --> 00:30.420
I SWEAR.
I DON'T KNOW YOU.

00:30.460 --> 00:31.722
UGH!

00:35.130 --> 00:36.722
Veronica:
THE WORD IS OUT.

00:36.770 --> 00:39.159
OUR ILLUSTRIOUS GUIDANCE
COUNSELOR HAS RECEIVED A GRANT

00:39.200 --> 00:42.499
TO STUDY THE LONG-TERM EFFECTS
OF GRIEF IN ADOLESCENTS.

00:42.540 --> 00:44.269
SHE'S DEMANDING AN AUDIENCE

00:44.310 --> 00:46.403
WITH EACH OF US HARDEST HIT
BY LILLY'S DEATH.

00:46.440 --> 00:48.328
I WAS GOING TO DECLINE
A SESSION.

00:48.380 --> 00:49.472
THEN I HAD A THOUGHT.

00:49.510 --> 00:50.670
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

00:56.250 --> 00:58.343
WELL, THERE'S SOMETHING
YOU DON'T SEE EVERY DAY.

00:59.620 --> 01:02.589
MAN, I CANNOT WAIT
TO GET OUT OF NEPTUNE.

01:02.630 --> 01:04.154
M.I.T., HUH?

01:04.190 --> 01:06.750
EARLY ADMISSION.

01:06.800 --> 01:09.769
BET YOU'RE GONNA MISS THIS PLACE
WHEN YOU'RE GONE.

01:09.800 --> 01:11.324
NOT REALLY.

01:11.370 --> 01:12.496
I DIDN'T THINK SO.

01:12.540 --> 01:13.768
VERONICA?

01:13.800 --> 01:15.665
SORRY TO MAKE YOU WAIT.
COME ON IN.

01:17.870 --> 01:21.237
DO YOU REMEMBER
WHEN WE TALKED LAST YEAR,

01:21.280 --> 01:23.248
RIGHT AFTER LILLY'S DEATH?

01:23.280 --> 01:25.544
YOU WERE INCONSOLABLE.

01:25.580 --> 01:28.674
I'M REALLY HOPING THAT THIS YEAR
YOU'RE ABLE TO TALK ABOUT IT.

01:28.720 --> 01:31.814
YOU KNOW, YOU'RE NEVER GONNA
COME TO TERMS WITH LILLY'S DEATH

01:31.850 --> 01:35.251
IF YOU KEEP ALL THAT PAIN
BOTI'LED UP INSIDE YOU.

01:35.290 --> 01:36.427
WOW.

01:36.460 --> 01:37.688
I HAVE THAT EXACT SAME

01:37.730 --> 01:39.755
PLATITUDE-A-DAY CALENDAR
AT HOME.

01:39.800 --> 01:42.325
IT'S HOW I KNOW
BEAUTY COMES FROM WITHIN.

01:42.370 --> 01:44.395
LOOK, VERONICA,
FOR WHATEVER REASON,

01:44.430 --> 01:46.864
I DON'T THINK
YOU CARE FOR ME VERY MUCH,

01:46.900 --> 01:49.460
SO IF YOU PREFER TALKING
WITH SOMEONE ELSE, THAT'S --

01:49.510 --> 01:51.398
[ STAPLER SNAPS ]

01:51.440 --> 01:53.579
SORRY.
THAT WAS RUDE.

01:53.610 --> 01:56.408
IT'S NOT YOU.
IT'S THE TALKING.

01:56.450 --> 01:58.748
I DON'T WANT TO TALK AWAY
MY GRIEF.

01:58.780 --> 02:01.442
I WANT TO TURN IT INTO
SOMETHING ELSE -- FUEL.

02:01.480 --> 02:03.448
I KNOW HOW I'M GONNA
FEEL BETTER,

02:03.490 --> 02:06.357
AND IT'S NOT BY TALKING
ABOUT HOW SAD I AM.

02:06.390 --> 02:07.584
[ STAPLER CLICKING ]

02:07.620 --> 02:08.712
VERONICA.

02:08.760 --> 02:11.752
YEAH, NERVOUS HABIT.

02:11.790 --> 02:14.190
[ STAPLER FALLS ]

02:17.230 --> 02:20.267
SO, HOW IS IT
YOU'RE GOING TO FIND, UH --

02:20.300 --> 02:22.768
I REALLY HATE
TO USE THIS WORD,

02:22.810 --> 02:24.630
BUT IT IS APPROPRIATE --

02:24.670 --> 02:25.864
CLOSURE?

02:27.940 --> 02:29.544
I'LL FIND CLOSURE

02:29.580 --> 02:31.707
WHEN LILLY'S KILLER'S
ROTI'ING AWAY IN PRISON.

02:38.420 --> 02:40.911
RICK, YOU'RE WANTED
IN THE OFFICE.

02:49.830 --> 02:51.388
THE SHERIFF IS HERE TO --

02:51.430 --> 02:53.864
MORNING, RICK.
HOW'S YOUR HEAD THIS MORNING?

02:53.900 --> 02:55.492
LITTLE BIT OF A HANGOVER?

02:57.570 --> 03:01.677
THAT'S NOTHING COMPARED TO HOW
YOUR BUDDY TIM IS FEELING.

03:01.710 --> 03:03.940
TIM HAD TO HAVE A TUBE
PUT DOWN HIS THROAT

03:03.980 --> 03:05.868
SO THEY COULD PUMP
HIS STOMACH.

03:05.910 --> 03:07.673
HE'S IN A COMA, RICK.

03:07.720 --> 03:10.280
OH, MY GOD.

03:10.320 --> 03:12.754
ACCORDING TO
A SURVEILLANCE TAPE,

03:12.790 --> 03:14.849
YOUR EVENING ENDED AT 1:30 A.M.,
WHEN YOU DROPPED --

03:14.890 --> 03:16.448
AND I MEAN DROPPED --

03:16.490 --> 03:19.425
AN UNCONSCIOUS TIM OUTSIDE
THE NEPTUNE MEMORIAL E.R.

03:19.460 --> 03:20.825
I DIDN'T HAVE A CHOICE.

03:23.400 --> 03:24.662
RIGHT.

03:24.700 --> 03:26.930
SOMEONE MUST HAVE
PUT A GUN TO YOUR HEAD,

03:26.970 --> 03:28.562
FORCED YOU ON A PUB CRAWL?

03:28.600 --> 03:31.831
BY THE WAY,
HOW DID YOU GET INTO THOSE BARS?

03:31.870 --> 03:34.430
WE GOT FAKE I.D.S.

03:34.480 --> 03:35.970
[ SIGHS ]

03:39.720 --> 03:41.711
YOU AND HALF THE KIDS
IN NEPTUNE.

03:41.750 --> 03:44.639
THESE THINGS HAVE BEEN
POPPING UP ALL OVER THE PLACE.

03:44.690 --> 03:47.488
THE WAY I SEE IT,
THEY'RE COMING FROM YOUR SCHOOL.

03:49.990 --> 03:52.322
I THINK YOU OWE IT
TO YOUR FRIEND

03:52.360 --> 03:54.328
TO TELL ME
WHO'S MAKING THE FAKES.

03:56.030 --> 03:58.419
LOOK, RICK...

04:00.040 --> 04:01.462
THE THREE OF US,

04:01.500 --> 04:03.536
WE'RE NOT LEAVING
THIS COZY LITTLE ROOM

04:03.570 --> 04:05.265
UNTIL YOU GIVE ME A NAME.

04:13.380 --> 04:15.371
VERONICA MARS.

04:25.760 --> 04:26.988
[ SIGHS ]

04:27.030 --> 04:29.498
SENDING OUT THE BIG GUNS
IN THE MORNING.

04:29.530 --> 04:30.963
I'M FLATTERED.

04:31.000 --> 04:33.696
THE SHERIFF WANTS TO HAVE A LOOK
INSIDE YOUR LOCKER.

04:33.740 --> 04:34.968
OF COURSE HE DOES.

04:35.000 --> 04:36.604
JUST OUT OF CURIOSITY,

04:36.640 --> 04:38.767
WHAT ARE YOU GENTLEMEN
HOPING TO FIND IN HERE?

04:38.810 --> 04:40.630
AL CAPONE?
THE LINDBERGH BABY?

04:40.680 --> 04:42.375
WE HAVE REASON TO BELIEVE

04:42.410 --> 04:44.401
THAT YOU ARE MANUFACTURING
AND DISTRIBUTING

04:44.450 --> 04:45.974
FAKE DRIVER'S LICENSES.

04:46.010 --> 04:47.375
OOH, THAT'S A NEW ONE.

04:47.420 --> 04:48.944
IT'S A SECOND-DEGREE
FELONY.

04:48.980 --> 04:50.982
LORD KNOWS I HATE
TO DISAPPOINT YOU BOYS.

04:55.420 --> 04:56.956
WAIT A MINUTE.
THOSE AREN'T MINE.

05:01.100 --> 05:03.660
I'M GONNA NEED TO SEARCH
YOUR PURSE, AS WELL.

05:03.700 --> 05:05.327
EITHER WE CAN DO THIS
HERE --

05:05.370 --> 05:07.429
OR DOWN AT THE STATION?

05:12.540 --> 05:13.677
[ SNIFFS ]

05:18.150 --> 05:20.038
LILLY KANE'S
DRIVER'S LICENSE.

05:20.080 --> 05:24.983
DRIVER'S LICENSE FOR...
A 22-YEAR-OLD VERONICA MARS.

05:26.420 --> 05:28.012
SAN DIEGO STATE
STUDENT I.D.

05:33.100 --> 05:35.819
LICENSED MASSAGE THERAPIST.

05:35.860 --> 05:38.067
OH, YEAH.
THOSE ARE MINE.

05:39.570 --> 05:41.834
YOU REALLY
DON'T HAVE TO DO THAT.

05:41.870 --> 05:43.633
BUT I'M GOING TO ANYWAY.

05:43.670 --> 05:46.833
DON'T BOTHER COMING BACK TO
SCHOOL FOR THE NEXT THREE DAYS.

05:46.880 --> 05:48.108
YOU'RE SUSPENDED.

05:48.140 --> 05:49.903
[ BELL RINGS ]

05:56.120 --> 05:59.453
Young man:
BE'I'I'ER CALL YOUR DADDY, MARS!

05:59.490 --> 06:02.550
NOW IT'S YOUR TURN, HUH?
HA HA!

06:07.730 --> 06:09.493
Young woman:
LATER, MARS.

06:09.530 --> 06:12.363
GOSH, I HOPE THEY USE
THAT SHOT IN THE YEARBOOK.

06:13.570 --> 06:17.563
* A LONG TIME AGO,
WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

06:17.610 --> 06:23.503
* BUT I HAVEN'T THOUGHT OF YOU
LATELY AT ALL *

06:23.550 --> 06:25.905
* COME ON, NOW, SUGAR

06:25.950 --> 06:28.578
* BRING IT ON, BRING IT ON,
YEAH *

06:28.620 --> 06:31.418
* JUST REMEMBER ME WHEN

06:31.450 --> 06:33.714
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS

06:33.760 --> 06:38.857
* A LONG TIME AGO,
WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

06:49.000 --> 06:50.638
KNOW ANY GOOD LAWYERS?

06:50.670 --> 06:52.206
VERY CUTE.

06:52.240 --> 06:55.073
I KNOW AN ADEQUATE ONE
WHO JUST POSTED YOUR $500 BAIL.

06:55.110 --> 06:57.169
THEY TAKE DINERS CLUB
HERE?

06:57.210 --> 06:59.075
SERIOUSLY, CLIFF, THANKS.

06:59.110 --> 07:01.749
IT'S ALL PART OF
MY FULL-SERVICE LEGAL COUNSEL.

07:01.780 --> 07:04.647
IS THERE ANY WAY YOU COULD
NOT TELL MY DAD ABOUT THIS?

07:04.690 --> 07:06.214
WHY DIDN'T YOU CALL HIM?

07:06.250 --> 07:08.582
HE'S CHASING A BAIL JUMPER
IN ARIZONA.

07:08.620 --> 07:11.088
YOUR DAD'S GONNA FIND OUT
ONE WAY OR THE OTHER.

07:11.130 --> 07:13.223
BESIDES, I MAY NEED
TO SIC HIM ON YOU

07:13.260 --> 07:15.820
IF YOU DON'T SHOW UP
NEXT TUESDAY, 9:00 AM.

07:15.860 --> 07:17.999
SO, ARE WE GONNA
BEAT THIS RAP?

07:18.030 --> 07:21.193
WELL, POSSESSION -- THEY'VE GOT
YOU PRETTY COLD ON THAT ONE.

07:21.240 --> 07:23.663
THE STUFF IN YOUR WALLET
IS MICKEY MOUSE.

07:23.710 --> 07:26.474
IT'S THE I.D.s IN THE LOCKER
THAT THEY CARE ABOUT.

07:26.510 --> 07:27.932
THEY WERE BLANK.

07:27.980 --> 07:30.175
SO, UNTIL THE COMA GUY WAKES UP,
THE ONLY THING THEY HAVE

07:30.210 --> 07:32.098
TYING YOU TO
THIS SUPPOSED FAKE-I.D. RING

07:32.150 --> 07:33.845
IS THE TESTIMONY
OF THE OTHER KID.

07:33.880 --> 07:34.869
WHAT OTHER KID?

07:34.920 --> 07:36.512
YOUR BUDDY...

07:36.550 --> 07:37.847
RICK.

07:37.890 --> 07:39.209
EXCUSE ME.

07:39.250 --> 07:41.252
MM-HMM.

07:41.290 --> 07:43.850
HOWDY, RICK.
DO I KNOW YOU?!

07:43.890 --> 07:45.528
NO.

07:45.560 --> 07:47.699
THEN WHY'D YOU TELL SHERIFF LAMB
I SOLD YOU A FAKE I.D.?

07:47.730 --> 07:49.789
IT'S -- IT'S WHAT
THEY TOLD ME TO SAY.

07:49.830 --> 07:50.797
WHO'S "THEY"?

07:50.830 --> 07:52.092
NO WAY.

07:52.130 --> 07:54.234
THEY'RE EVERYWHERE.
THEY WILL DESTROY ME.

07:54.270 --> 07:55.760
I'LL DESTROY YOU WORSE.

07:55.800 --> 07:57.836
I CAN'T TALK ABOUT IT
HERE.

07:57.870 --> 07:59.735
TOMORROW IN SCHOOL,
WE TALK.

07:59.780 --> 08:01.998
NO, I TOLD YOU --
IT HAS TO BE DONE IN SECRET.

08:02.040 --> 08:03.268
OH, IT WILL BE.

08:03.310 --> 08:05.699
YOU'LL BE HEARING
FROM ME.

08:05.750 --> 08:07.741
I THOUGHT
YOU WERE EXPELLED.

08:09.120 --> 08:12.146
LA FEMME VERONICA.

08:12.190 --> 08:15.159
I HEARD IT TOOK
THREE OFFICERS AND A STUN GUN

08:15.190 --> 08:17.579
TO HAUL YOUR BUTT
OUT OF SCHOOL.

08:17.630 --> 08:20.895
YOU MUST BE THE ONLY STUDENT
WHO DIDN'T SEE MY WALK OF SHAME.

08:20.930 --> 08:22.761
I GRABBED YOUR BOOKS...

08:22.800 --> 08:24.995
AND YOUR HOMEWORK
FROM YOUR TEACHERS.

08:25.030 --> 08:26.861
I NEED TO ASK
ANOTHER FAVOR.

08:26.900 --> 08:29.903
THIS BETTER INVOLVE ME
SEDUCING THE HEAD CHEERLEADER.

08:29.940 --> 08:32.670
I NEED YOU TO SEE
IF YOU CAN GET ME A FAKE I.D.

08:32.710 --> 08:34.974
IF YOU MUST SEDUCE
THE HEAD CHEERLEADER

08:35.010 --> 08:37.171
TO ACCOMPLISH YOUR MISSION,
SO BE IT.

08:37.210 --> 08:38.199
NO SWEAT.

08:39.650 --> 08:40.776
HOW DO I DO THAT?

08:40.820 --> 08:42.173
PLAY ON HER INSECURITY.

08:42.220 --> 08:43.744
I MEANT
THE FAKE I.D. PART.

08:43.790 --> 08:45.280
OKAY,
LET'S PRETEND FOR A MOMENT

08:45.320 --> 08:47.618
THAT THIS MYTHICAL
HEAD CHEERLEADER OF YOURS

08:47.660 --> 08:49.184
HAS JUST ASKED YOU
OUT ON A DATE.

08:49.220 --> 08:51.757
IN EXCHANGE
FOR SEVEN MINUTES IN HEAVEN,

08:51.790 --> 08:54.293
YOU HAVE TO GET HER INTO
THE HOTTEST NIGHTCLUB IN NEPTUNE

08:54.330 --> 08:56.924
OR AT LEAST BUY HER A PACK
OF STRAWBERRY WINE COOLERS.

08:56.970 --> 08:59.063
THE STAKES ARE HIGH,
WALLACE FENNEL.

08:59.100 --> 09:01.534
THINK, NOW --
HOW WOULD YOU DO IT?

09:07.110 --> 09:09.078
HEY, VERONICA.

09:09.110 --> 09:10.338
YEAH?

09:10.380 --> 09:13.144
I NEED YOU TO GET ME
A FAKE I.D.

09:13.180 --> 09:17.310
SO I CAN GET SOME FAKE ACTION
FROM A FAKE CHEERLEADER.

09:17.350 --> 09:19.341
WALLACE...

09:30.270 --> 09:32.261
Man on radio:
IF YOU'RE BREATHING,

09:32.300 --> 09:34.359
THEN YOU'VE HEARD
ABOUT AARON ECHOLLS

09:34.400 --> 09:36.664
GETTING GINSUED
AT HIS OWN CHRISTMAS PARTY.

09:36.710 --> 09:39.133
Man #2: EXPLAIN WHY A GUY
WHO'S MARRIED TO LYNN ECHOLLS

09:39.170 --> 09:41.035
WOULD WANT TO BANG
THE FREAKIN' HELP!

09:41.080 --> 09:43.344
IT'S LIKE THE SAYING GOES --
"SHOW ME A HOT CHICK,

09:43.380 --> 09:45.940
"AND I'LL SHOW YOU A GUY
WHO'S TIRED OF HITTING THAT."

09:45.980 --> 09:47.242
[ KNOCK ON WINDOW ]
LOGAN.

09:47.280 --> 09:48.838
YEAH, BE RIGHT THERE.

09:50.420 --> 09:54.652
* WITH BROKEN WORDS
IN MONOTONE *

09:54.690 --> 09:59.229
* JUST SMILE
AND TAKE THE PICTURE *

09:59.260 --> 10:03.128
* NOTHING HURTS
UNTIL IT'S GONE *

10:03.170 --> 10:07.334
* MY NEW YEAR'S RESOLUTION

10:09.710 --> 10:12.702
* 'CAUSE ALL
THEY EVER DO IS... *

10:12.740 --> 10:16.369
* AH-AH-AH-AH

10:20.280 --> 10:23.738
IN MY HUMBLE OPINION,
YOUR MOM'S TOTALLY HOTTER.

10:23.790 --> 10:24.916
SHUT THE HELL UP!

10:26.420 --> 10:28.354
BIG MISTAKE, SON.

10:28.390 --> 10:29.618
UGH!

10:30.830 --> 10:32.229
[ LAUGHS ]

10:36.360 --> 10:37.861
BREAK IT UP!

10:37.900 --> 10:39.162
BREAK IT UP!

10:39.200 --> 10:40.633
NO!

10:45.840 --> 10:47.330
TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH,

10:47.380 --> 10:50.042
I REALLY DON'T REMEMBER
THAT WEEK.

10:50.080 --> 10:53.311
HMM. YOU DON'T REMEMBER
BEING IN THIS OFFICE?

10:53.350 --> 10:55.875
YOU SLAMMED THE CHAIR
AGAINST THE WALL, ELI.

10:55.920 --> 10:57.808
[ SIGHS ]
THE LAST TIME WE MET,

10:57.850 --> 11:00.318
IT SEEMED LIKE LILLY'S DEATH
HAD AFFECTED YOU

11:00.360 --> 11:01.816
IN QUITE A PROFOUND WAY.

11:01.860 --> 11:03.418
WELL, YEAH.
I WAS MAD.

11:03.460 --> 11:06.998
YOU KNOW, THE SAME DAY
LILLY KANE DIED,

11:07.030 --> 11:09.760
A LITTLE GIRL WENT MISSING
IN MY NEIGHBORHOOD.

11:09.800 --> 11:14.066
THEY FOUND HER BODY
THREE MONTHS LATER.

11:14.100 --> 11:16.068
WHERE WERE THE CAMERAS
WHEN SHE WENT MISSING?

11:16.100 --> 11:18.432
WHERE WAS THE GRIEF COUNSELING
FOR HER?

11:18.470 --> 11:22.133
WHAT HAPPENED TO MARIS
WAS A TRAGEDY. PEOPLE DO CARE.

11:22.180 --> 11:23.875
[ RADIO TUNING ]

11:23.910 --> 11:26.276
BUT RIGHT NOW, I JUST WANT
TO TALK ABOUT LILLY, OKAY?

11:26.310 --> 11:28.119
OH, WELL,
THEN WHY DON'T YOU CALL

11:28.150 --> 11:30.141
SOME OF HER RICH,
WHITE FRIENDS IN HERE?

11:30.190 --> 11:31.987
I WANT YOU TO LISTEN
TO SOMETHING.

11:32.020 --> 11:34.352
IT'S A LETTER YOU WROTE.

11:34.390 --> 11:36.881
"YOU TORE MY HEART OUT.

11:36.930 --> 11:39.899
"YOU CAN ACT LIKE WHAT WE HAD
TOGETHER MEANT NOTHING TO YOU,

11:39.930 --> 11:42.023
"BUT YOU CAN'T STOP ME
FROM LOVING YOU.

11:42.060 --> 11:44.199
"FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE,
WHEREVER YOU GO,

11:44.230 --> 11:45.424
"I'LL ALWAYS BE THERE,

11:45.470 --> 11:49.133
JUST OUT OF SIGHT,
IN THE SHADOWS."

11:49.170 --> 11:52.037
YOU KNOW, I DON'T REMEMBER
C.C.-ing YOU ON THAT.

11:52.070 --> 11:54.903
LILLY WANTED TO BE TRANSFERRED
OUT OF YOUR P.E. CLASS.

11:54.940 --> 11:56.874
SHE WAS HAVING TROUBLE
WITH A BOY.

11:56.910 --> 11:58.707
SHE GAVE ME THESE
TO PROVE IT.

12:01.350 --> 12:03.238
I NEVER WOULD HAVE
HURT HER.

12:05.050 --> 12:07.484
THE COPS RUBBED MY NOSE
IN THOSE LETTERS, SO WHAT...

12:07.520 --> 12:09.454
Veronica:
LILLY AND WEEVIL?

12:09.490 --> 12:12.926
LOOK, ELI, I DIDN'T BRING YOU
IN HERE TO EMBARRASS YOU.

12:12.960 --> 12:14.154
I INVITED YOU IN HERE

12:14.200 --> 12:16.225
TO TALK ABOUT
WHY YOU WROTE THESE THINGS.

12:19.170 --> 12:23.834
HER AND LOGAN
HAD JUST BROKEN UP.

12:23.870 --> 12:27.328
AND LILLY SWORE TO ME
THAT SHE'D NEVER GO BACK TO HIM,

12:27.380 --> 12:29.371
BUT THEN...

12:29.410 --> 12:31.446
ONE DAY, THAT PUNK
SNAPS HIS FINGERS,

12:31.480 --> 12:33.948
AND ALL OF A SUDDEN,

12:33.980 --> 12:37.438
IT'S LIKE WE DON'T EVEN
KNOW EACH OTHER ANYMORE.

12:39.490 --> 12:41.856
IT'S...

12:41.890 --> 12:46.554
SHE WAS SOMEONE
I COULD HAVE LOVED, YOU KNOW?

12:46.590 --> 12:49.320
AND SHE FELT IT, TOO.
I KNOW SHE DID.

12:51.400 --> 12:55.063
WHY DIDN'T LILLY
TELL ME ABOUT HIM?

12:55.100 --> 12:57.432
WAS WEEVIL HER BIG SECRET?

12:57.470 --> 13:00.030
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

13:00.080 --> 13:02.378
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

13:02.410 --> 13:03.809
HELLO?

13:03.850 --> 13:05.203
BACK PARKING LOT,
FOURTH ROW.

13:10.550 --> 13:11.881
WHERE ARE YOU?

13:11.920 --> 13:13.080
IS ANYONE WATCHING YOU?

13:13.120 --> 13:14.109
I DON'T THINK SO.

13:14.160 --> 13:15.889
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

13:19.390 --> 13:21.221
SLIDE ON IN.

13:28.170 --> 13:31.003
SO, WHERE WERE WE?
RIGHT -- WHO FRAMED ME?

13:31.040 --> 13:32.905
THEY'RE CALLED THE TRITONS.

13:32.940 --> 13:35.272
IT'S A SECRET SOCIETY
AT SCHOOL.

13:35.310 --> 13:37.141
WHY HAVEN'T
I HEARD OF THEM?

13:37.180 --> 13:39.000
THAT'S A STUPID QUESTION.

13:39.050 --> 13:40.870
KEEP GOING.

13:40.920 --> 13:43.548
THE TRITONS HAVE BEEN AROUND
AS LONG AS NEPTUNE HIGH.

13:43.590 --> 13:46.286
SIX NEW MEMBERS
ARE INDUCTED THEIR JUNIOR YEAR

13:46.320 --> 13:47.548
BY THE SIX SENIORS.

13:47.590 --> 13:49.922
TIM AND I
WERE AMONG THEIR PLEDGES.

13:49.960 --> 13:51.279
WHO'S IN CHARGE?

13:51.330 --> 13:54.026
NO ONE EVEN KNOWS FOR SURE
WHO THE BROTHERS ARE.

13:54.060 --> 13:56.051
THEN WHO INVITED YOU
TO JOIN?

13:56.100 --> 13:59.263
TWO WEEKS AGO,
I FOUND A NOTE IN MY LOCKER.

14:14.350 --> 14:16.375
SO THIS WAS ALL PART
OF A HAZING RITUAL?

14:16.420 --> 14:17.887
THE 12 LABORS.

14:17.920 --> 14:20.081
THE FIRST FEW CHALLENGES
WEREN'T SO BAD,

14:20.120 --> 14:22.350
BUT ON FRIDAY,
WHEN I OPENED UP MY LOCKER,

14:22.390 --> 14:25.359
I FOUND A FAKE I.D. WITH
MY YEARBOOK PICTURE ON IT.

14:25.390 --> 14:28.928
WE WERE TO GO TO A BUNCH OF BARS
AND HAVE A SHOT AT EACH OF THEM.

14:28.960 --> 14:30.598
LET ME GUESS -- 12?

14:30.630 --> 14:32.268
TIM PASSED OUT
AT THE 11th.

14:32.300 --> 14:34.165
ALL THE OTHER PLEDGES
FREAKED OUT

14:34.200 --> 14:36.191
AND LEI-T ME THERE
TO TAKE CARE OF HIM,

14:36.240 --> 14:37.639
SO I THREW HIM
IN THE CAR,

14:37.670 --> 14:40.207
AND I TOOK HIM THE HOSPITAL
AS FAST AS I COULD.

14:40.240 --> 14:42.572
IF THEY'RE SO SECRET,
HOW DO YOU KNOW ALL THIS?

14:42.610 --> 14:44.646
MY DAD WAS A TRITON.

14:44.680 --> 14:47.240
SO WERE
MY TWO OLDER BROTHERS.

14:56.090 --> 14:59.582
ALL I CARED ABOUT AT THAT MOMENT
WAS STAYING ON THEIR GOOD SIDE.

14:59.630 --> 15:03.225
IF THEY FOUND OUT THAT
I BETRAYED THEIR SECRETS...

15:03.270 --> 15:05.226
LET'S JUST SAY
I'D BE BETTER OFF IN JAIL.

15:05.270 --> 15:06.464
THESE GUYS WILL DESTROY
YOUR LIFE.

15:06.500 --> 15:08.229
IT'S THEIR
MISSION STATEMENT.

15:08.270 --> 15:10.409
THAT'S YOUR DEFENSE --
YOU WERE JUST FOLLOWING ORDERS?

15:10.440 --> 15:12.408
[ IMITATES BUZZER ]
THAT DOESN'T CUT IT, RICK!

15:12.440 --> 15:14.635
I KNOW THAT NOW,
AND I'M SORRY.

15:14.680 --> 15:16.409
YOU'VE GOT TO BELIEVE ME.

15:16.440 --> 15:18.476
AI-TER WHAT THEY DID
TO TIM?

15:18.510 --> 15:21.274
AND NOW HIS FAMILY'S
THREATENING TO SUE ME.

15:21.320 --> 15:23.515
I CAN'T EVEN TALK
TO MY OWN DAD ABOUT IT.

15:23.550 --> 15:27.213
HE CALLS ME A COWARD
AND A TRAITOR FOR WHAT I DID,

15:27.260 --> 15:29.251
BUT HOW COULD I BELONG
TO A CLUB

15:29.290 --> 15:31.383
THAT ALMOST KILLED
MY BEST FRIEND?

15:31.430 --> 15:34.490
ALL I WANT NOW
IS FOR THE TRITONS TO GO DOWN.

15:34.530 --> 15:36.054
SO, WHO ARE
THE OTHER PLEDGES?

15:36.100 --> 15:37.567
ANYONE WHO'S ANYONE.

15:37.600 --> 15:40.569
THE TRITON SUPPOSEDLY CHOOSE
THE BEST GUYS IN EVERYTHING --

15:40.600 --> 15:42.739
ACADEMICS, SPORTS.

15:42.770 --> 15:45.500
THEY'RE PRETTY MUCH
THE SIX GUYS YOU'D EXPECT.

15:45.540 --> 15:47.132
I WANT THEIR NAMES.

15:47.180 --> 15:50.149
HARRY DIDDEN...

15:50.180 --> 15:52.000
STEVE VARGO...

15:52.050 --> 15:53.540
MATT BARONE...

15:53.580 --> 15:55.514
DUNCAN KANE.

15:58.490 --> 16:02.085
SO, IF I FOLLOW DUNCAN,
I CAN FIND THE TRITONS.

16:07.660 --> 16:09.127
[ BEEP ]

16:19.110 --> 16:20.600
THAN KS.
I APPRECIATE IT.

16:20.640 --> 16:22.198
LOGAN, LET'S GO.

16:22.240 --> 16:24.208
HOW LONG DID I GET?

16:24.250 --> 16:26.309
YOU'RE NOT
BEING SUSPENDED.

16:26.350 --> 16:29.012
THE VICE PRINCIPAL WANTS ALL
THREE OF US BACK HERE ON FRIDAY

16:29.050 --> 16:31.610
FOR A DISCIPLINARY
CONFERENCE.

16:31.650 --> 16:35.051
LISTEN, I'M NOT HAPPY
THAT YOU WERE FIGHTING,

16:35.090 --> 16:37.354
BUT I AM PROUD OF YOU
FOR STICKING UP FOR YOUR MOTHER.

16:37.390 --> 16:38.687
YOU'RE PROUD OF ME?

16:38.730 --> 16:40.721
OH, GREAT. GOOD.
I CAN DIE HAPPY.

16:42.430 --> 16:45.263
YOU KEEP SMARTING OFF,
AND I'LL HELP ARRANGE IT.

16:46.530 --> 16:48.669
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

16:52.110 --> 16:54.203
SORRY, CLIFF, I'M LATE.

16:57.250 --> 16:58.706
HI, DAD.

16:58.750 --> 17:01.514
THEIR CASE IS FUZZY
AND CIRCUMSTANTIAL.

17:04.220 --> 17:06.211
THOSE WERE ALSO
HER VERY FIRST WORDS.

17:06.250 --> 17:09.754
I THINK I'VE GOT A GOOD LEAD
ON WHO'S MAKING THE FAKE I.D.s.

17:09.790 --> 17:12.452
IT'S A SECRET SOCIETY AT SCHOOL
CALLED THE TRITONS.

17:12.490 --> 17:15.220
RICK TOLD ME HE WAS BULLIED
INTO TURNING ME IN.

17:15.260 --> 17:18.593
I'M POSITIVE THEY'RE THE ONES
WHO SET THE BLANKS IN MY LOCKER.

17:18.630 --> 17:22.168
THE CRIMINAL CASE IS
THE LEAST OF OUR PROBLEMS.

17:22.200 --> 17:23.804
TIM'S PARENTS ARE SUING.

17:23.840 --> 17:25.239
US?

17:25.270 --> 17:26.828
AND PRETTY MUCH
EVERYONE ELSE INVOLVED

17:26.870 --> 17:28.633
IN THEIR SON'S
NIGHT OF DEBAUCHERY.

17:28.680 --> 17:31.547
EVERY BAR IN TOWN
IS GONNA BE NAMED IN THE SUIT.

17:31.580 --> 17:34.515
THE THING
COULD BE WORTH MILLIONS.

17:44.760 --> 17:46.682
AARON.

17:46.730 --> 17:48.698
COME ON IN.

17:48.730 --> 17:50.698
HEY, KEITH.

17:50.730 --> 17:53.733
SO, HOW'S IT GOING?
YOU NEED ANYTHING?

17:53.770 --> 17:57.558
UH...YEAH,
SOME WATER WOULD BE GOOD.

17:57.610 --> 17:59.532
SO, I, UH...

17:59.570 --> 18:02.676
I GUESS I SHOULD HAVE CANCELED
THAT PARTY AI-TER ALL, HUH?

18:04.710 --> 18:06.302
THAN KS.

18:06.350 --> 18:08.147
HOW YOU HANGING IN?

18:11.190 --> 18:14.284
THIS, I CAN HANDLE.

18:14.320 --> 18:16.811
BUT THESE...

18:16.860 --> 18:19.283
I'VE BEEN TRYING TO REGAIN
MY FAMILY'S TRUST,

18:19.330 --> 18:21.321
AND I MEANT WHAT I SAID
WHEN I TOLD YOU

18:21.360 --> 18:23.294
THAT I WAS GONNA
GIVE UP ALL OF THAT.

18:23.330 --> 18:24.729
BUT THESE STORIES --

18:24.770 --> 18:27.136
I MEAN, THEY'RE TEARING
MY FAMILY APART.

18:27.170 --> 18:30.401
MY DAUGHTER TRINA'S THE ONLY ONE
THAT'LL TALK TO ME ANYMORE.

18:30.440 --> 18:32.431
I CAN'T BLAME LOGAN
OR HIS MOTHER.

18:32.470 --> 18:35.405
I JUST...

18:35.440 --> 18:40.139
ANY IDEA WHO COULD KNOW
SUCH INTIMATE DETAILS ABOUT YOU?

18:42.220 --> 18:43.778
PAPARAZZI.

18:43.820 --> 18:46.744
THEN AGAIN, THEY WOULD HAVE
PRINTED THE STORIES RIGHT AWAY.

18:48.860 --> 18:50.327
SOMEONE ON MY STAFF?

18:50.360 --> 18:53.625
JEALOUS BOYFRIEND
OR HUSBAND?

18:53.660 --> 18:55.719
AH, IT'S A POSSIBILITY.

18:55.760 --> 18:58.490
[ SIGHS ]

18:58.530 --> 19:00.191
WELL, LET ME DIG AROUND.

19:00.240 --> 19:01.832
LISTEN...

19:03.840 --> 19:06.832
MY WIFE'S REALLY FRAGILE.

19:06.870 --> 19:09.532
I DON'T KNOW HOW MUCH MORE
SCANDAL SHE CAN TAKE.

19:11.610 --> 19:14.477
LET ME SEE WHAT I CAN DO.

19:14.520 --> 19:18.513
"TRITON -- SON OF NEPTUNE,
THE GOD OF THE SEA.

19:18.550 --> 19:21.485
"WITH HIS GREAT HORN,
TRITON COMMANDS THE DARK WATERS

19:21.520 --> 19:23.624
"AND ALL THE CREATURES
WITHIN."

