COMES INTO SAC-N-PAC,

19:37.640 --> 19:39.608
BUYS A 6-PACK FROM MY BOSS
LIKE IT WAS NO PROBLEM.

19:39.640 --> 19:41.608
DID YOU FIGURE OUT
WHERE HE GOT HIS FAKE?

19:41.640 --> 19:43.369
SLOW DOWN.
THIS IS MY STORY.

19:44.410 --> 19:46.571
I FOLLOWED HIM OUT
TO THE PARKING LOT,

19:46.610 --> 19:49.613
AND I WAS LIKE, "YO, FELLA,
YOU'RE ON 'CANDID CAMERA."'

19:49.650 --> 19:51.288
PFI', PFI'!

19:51.320 --> 19:54.380
GAVE HIM THE 4-1-1 ON OUR
VIDEO PLAYBACK CAPABILITIES,

19:54.420 --> 19:57.423
YOU KNOW, LEANED ON HIM,
GOT ALL SHAFT OR SOMETHING.

19:57.460 --> 19:58.449
SHUT YOUR MOUTH!

19:58.490 --> 19:59.525
LONG STORY SHORT...

19:59.560 --> 20:00.925
HA!

20:00.960 --> 20:02.825
THE GUY CLAIMED THERE'S
A MYSTERY LOCKER AT SCHOOL.

20:02.860 --> 20:04.794
OOH, I LIKE IT ALREADY.

20:04.830 --> 20:07.230
YOU PUT YOUR NAME AND 250 BUCKS
IN LOCKER 110

20:07.270 --> 20:08.669
FIRST THING
IN THE MORNING.

20:08.700 --> 20:10.804
COME AFTERNOON,
BRAND-SPANKING-NEW LICENSE

20:10.840 --> 20:13.570
THAT SAYS YOU WERE BORN IN 1983
ARRIVES IN YOUR LOCKER.

20:13.610 --> 20:16.272
ARE YOU WILLING TO PUT $250
INTO SOME STRANGE LOCKER

20:16.310 --> 20:17.538
TO SEE IF THIS WORKS?

20:17.580 --> 20:18.877
HELL NO.

20:18.910 --> 20:21.470
I'M USING YOUR MONEY.

20:21.520 --> 20:23.385
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:23.420 --> 20:25.581
[ CLEANER RUNNING ]

20:28.620 --> 20:31.680
HOW MANY TIMES HAVE I WALKED
THROUGH THE MAIN HALLWAY,

20:31.730 --> 20:33.925
AND HOW MANY TIMES
HAVE I NOT NOTICED

20:33.960 --> 20:36.793
THAT OUR SCHOOL'S INSIGNIA
INCLUDES TRITON'S CONCH SHELL?

20:44.470 --> 20:46.006
ACCORDING TO WALLACE,

20:46.040 --> 20:49.407
LOCKER 110 ISN'T ASSIGNED
TO ANYONE IN SCHOOL,

20:49.440 --> 20:51.601
BUT CLEARLY,
SOMEONE HAS THE COMBINATION.

20:51.650 --> 20:54.574
IF ALL ONE HAS TO DO IN ORDER
TO PROCURE A FAKE I.D.

20:54.620 --> 20:58.340
IS SLIP CASH IN LOCKER 110,
IT STANDS TO REASON

20:58.390 --> 21:00.858
ALL I HAVE TO DO
IS SEE WHO OPENS SAID LOCKER.

21:00.890 --> 21:03.757
THIS IS MADE TOUGHER,
THOUGH NOT IMPOSSIBLE,

21:03.790 --> 21:06.588
BY MY SUSPENSION.

21:16.000 --> 21:19.458
THEN WALLACE WILL DROP THE $250
IN THE MYSTERY LOCKER.

21:19.510 --> 21:21.501
[ DOOR OPENS ]

21:21.540 --> 21:23.405
THANKS FOR COMING IN,
LOGAN.

21:23.450 --> 21:26.442
THANKS FOR GETTING ME
OUT OF A CALCULUS TEST, BECKY.

21:26.480 --> 21:27.970
IT'S "MISS JAMES," PLEASE.

21:28.020 --> 21:29.715
SO, THE WEEK LILLY DIED

21:29.750 --> 21:31.843
WOULD HAVE BEEN
OUR SECOND ANNIVERSARY.

21:31.890 --> 21:34.415
WE WERE TOGETHER
SINCE JUNIOR HIGH.

21:34.460 --> 21:35.916
OFF AND ON?

21:35.960 --> 21:37.882
YEAH, OFF AND ON.

21:37.930 --> 21:39.921
AND AT THE TIME
OF HER MURDER, YOU WERE...

21:39.960 --> 21:42.326
OFF.

21:42.360 --> 21:44.521
TEMPORARILY.

21:44.570 --> 21:46.026
WHY WERE YOU BROKEN UP?

21:46.070 --> 21:50.029
WE WERE SUPPOSED TO GO
TO THIS PARTY.

21:50.070 --> 21:53.335
AND LILLY WAS PISSED AT ME
FOR SOMETHING.

21:53.380 --> 21:55.598
I CAN'T EVEN REMEMBER WHAT,
YOU KNOW?

21:55.640 --> 21:58.006
AND, UH...

21:58.050 --> 21:59.802
LILLY STANDS ME UP.

21:59.850 --> 22:01.875
I END UP GETTING
PRETTY HAMMERED

22:01.920 --> 22:04.912
AND WIND UP KISSING
THIS OTHER GIRL

22:04.950 --> 22:06.918
FOR LIKE THREE SECONDS.

22:06.950 --> 22:08.508
AND LILLY SAW YOU TWO?

22:08.560 --> 22:10.357
NOPE.
SOMEONE ELSE DID.

22:10.390 --> 22:12.051
YOU MUST KNOW HER.

22:12.090 --> 22:14.957
WORD IS YOU'RE REAL CLOSE
WITH HER DAD.

22:15.000 --> 22:16.558
YOU COULD DO BETTER.

22:16.600 --> 22:18.921
YOU NEED TO LEAVE
MY PERSONAL LIFE OUT OF THIS.

22:18.970 --> 22:20.767
LET'S NOT GET PERSONAL
ABOUT THIS.

22:20.800 --> 22:23.963
YOU KNOW WHAT? IT SOUNDS LIKE
YOU BLAME VERONICA.

22:24.010 --> 22:26.035
YOU KNOW, VERONICA WAS
MY FRIEND, TOO,

22:26.070 --> 22:28.072
AND IF SHE HADN'T
RATTED ME OUT,

22:28.110 --> 22:30.908
THEN LILLY AND I
WOULD HAVE STAYED TOGETHER.

22:30.950 --> 22:34.408
AND LILLY WOULDN'T HAVE BEEN
ALONE THAT DAY.

22:34.450 --> 22:37.749
I WOULD HAVE BEEN THERE.

22:37.790 --> 22:39.849
SO YEAH,
I BLAME VERONICA.

22:43.120 --> 22:45.452
[ SIGHS ] AND I BLAME MYSELF
FOR BEING STUPID,

22:45.490 --> 22:48.391
AND I BLAME LILLY
FOR BEING A BITCH THAT WEEK.

22:48.430 --> 22:52.719
YOU KNOW, THERE IS ANOTHER WAY
OF LOOKING AT THIS, LOGAN.

22:52.770 --> 22:55.568
IF YOU'D STILL BEEN TOGETHER,
YOU MIGHT BE DEAD, TOO.

22:55.600 --> 22:56.862
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:56.900 --> 22:59.130
AND WHAT IS SO GREAT
ABOUT LIVING?

23:01.740 --> 23:03.708
[ BEEPING ]

23:03.750 --> 23:04.978
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

23:05.010 --> 23:06.841
HEY, WALLACE.
HOW WAS PRACTICE?

23:06.880 --> 23:08.916
I WAS ON FIRE
OUT THERE!

23:08.950 --> 23:10.986
3-POINT LINE,
HAND IN MY FACE,

23:11.020 --> 23:13.682
FADE AWAY LIKE JORDAN,
BOOM!

23:13.720 --> 23:14.880
GREAT.

23:14.920 --> 23:16.888
YOU'RE NOT LISTENING
TO A WORD I SAY.

23:16.920 --> 23:20.151
I MIGHT AS WELL HAVE SAID,
"BLAH BLAH BLABBITY BLAH BLAH."

23:20.190 --> 23:21.748
MM-HMM.

23:21.800 --> 23:23.597
HOW'D YOU LIKE TO GO
ON A LITTLE FIELD TRIP?

23:23.630 --> 23:25.598
DUNCAN'S ON THE MOVE,
AND IF WE HURRY,

23:25.630 --> 23:28.064
WE MIGHT MAKE IT FOR THE
BRANDING AND BLOOD SACRIFICE.

23:28.100 --> 23:30.159
ACTUALLY, I PLANNED ON
HITTING A FEW BARS.

23:30.200 --> 23:34.899
I FOUND THIS LITTLE BEAUTY IN
MY LOCKER AFTER SEVENTH PERIOD.

23:34.940 --> 23:36.635
LET ME SEE THAT.

23:36.680 --> 23:38.739
THE INK IS BLEEDING
AT THE EDGES.

23:38.780 --> 23:42.739
THE HOLOGRAM IS MISSING,
AND THE PHOTO...

23:42.780 --> 23:44.816
IS THAT YOUR YEARBOOK PICTURE,
WALLACE?

23:44.850 --> 23:46.010
SO WHAT?

23:46.050 --> 23:48.883
SO THIS IS
A $250 PIECE OF CRAP.

23:48.920 --> 23:51.821
NOW I'M NOT JUST
FALSELY ACCUSED.

23:51.860 --> 23:53.748
I'M GENUINELY OFFENDED.

23:53.800 --> 23:55.791
ALL I'VE HEARD --
THESE GUYS ARE BAD NEWS,

23:55.830 --> 23:57.798
SO I WANT YOU
TO BE CAREFUL.

