25:09.640 --> 25:11.699
THIS IS GOING NOWHERE.

25:12.640 --> 25:14.574
HEADS UP.

25:14.610 --> 25:18.102
LOOKS LIKE YOUR BOY'S
HAVING SECOND THOUGHTS.

25:18.150 --> 25:19.276
ARE YOU READY TO TALK?

25:25.320 --> 25:28.118
"THE JUDGES HOLD
THE VITAL SCORES.

25:28.160 --> 25:31.049
"YOU SHALL HEAR MY VOICE
ONCE I'VE HEARD YOURS.

25:31.090 --> 25:33.126
