I'LL GETCHA *

26:52.440 --> 26:54.874
* ONE WAY OR ANOTHER

26:54.910 --> 26:56.639
* I'M GONNA SEE YA

26:56.680 --> 26:58.272
* I'M GONNA MEETCHA, MEETCHA,
MEETCHA, MEETCHA *

26:58.310 --> 27:00.778
* ONE DAY, MAYBE NEXT WEEK

27:00.820 --> 27:02.173
* I'M GONNA MEETCHA

27:02.220 --> 27:04.415
* I'M GONNA MEETCHA,
I'LL MEETCHA *

27:04.450 --> 27:07.419
* I'LL WALK DOWN THE MALL,
STAND OVER BY THE WALL *

27:07.450 --> 27:10.317
* WHERE I CAN SEE IT ALL,
FIND OUT WHO YA CALL *

27:10.360 --> 27:12.419
* LEAD YOU TO
THE SUPERMARKET CHECKOUT *

27:12.460 --> 27:16.157
* SEE SOME SPECIALS AND RAP
AND GET LOST IN THE CROWD *

27:16.200 --> 27:18.896
* ONE WAY OR ANOTHER

27:18.930 --> 27:20.739
* I'M GONNA GETCHA, GETCHA,
GETCHA, GETCHA *

27:20.770 --> 27:22.431
* GETCHA, GETCHA,
GETCHA, GETCHA *

27:22.470 --> 27:24.768
* ONE WAY OR ANOTHER

27:24.810 --> 27:26.266
* I'M GONNA GETCHA,
I'LL GETCHA *

27:26.310 --> 27:28.403
* I'LL GETCHA, GETCHA,
GETCHA, GETCHA *

27:28.440 --> 27:30.772
* ONE WAY OR ANOTHER

27:30.810 --> 27:32.448
* I'M GONNA GETCHA,
I'LL GETCHA *

27:32.480 --> 27:34.175
* I'LL GETCHA, GETCHA,
GETCHA, GETCHA *

27:34.220 --> 27:36.438
* ONE WAY OR ANOTHER

27:36.480 --> 27:38.289
* I'M GONNA GETCHA,
I'LL GETCHA *

27:38.320 --> 27:40.117
* I'LL GETCHA, GETCHA,
GETCHA, GETCHA *

27:40.150 --> 27:42.357
* ONE WAY OR ANOTHER

27:42.390 --> 27:44.358
* I'M GONNA GETCHA,
I'LL GETCHA *

27:44.390 --> 27:45.926
* I'LL GETCHA, GETCHA,
GETCHA, GETCHA *

27:45.960 --> 27:47.791
* ONE WAY

27:47.830 --> 27:49.798
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

27:51.800 --> 27:53.665
THANK YOU.

28:00.470 --> 28:02.938
LET'S HEAR IT
FOR VERONICA MARS!

28:10.480 --> 28:12.084
HELLO?

28:12.120 --> 28:16.216
[ Distorted voice ]
THE GREAT TRITON IS LISTENING.

28:16.260 --> 28:18.478
I WANT TO KNOW
WHY YOU PLANTED

28:18.530 --> 28:21.158
ALL THOSE FAKE I.D.S
IN MY LOCKER.

28:21.200 --> 28:25.227
THE GREAT TRITON DID THAT TO YOU
BECAUSE HE'S GREAT.

28:25.270 --> 28:26.794
YEAH, YOU'RE A REAL PAL,

28:26.830 --> 28:29.094
UNLESS YOU NEED A RIDE
TO THE HOSPITAL.

28:29.140 --> 28:32.234
THE GREAT TRITON
DOESN'T REALLY KNOW

28:32.270 --> 28:34.738
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

28:37.410 --> 28:39.105
WHO ARE YOU?

28:39.150 --> 28:40.208
JEFF.

28:40.250 --> 28:41.376
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
IN HERE?

28:41.420 --> 28:43.980
SOME DUDE,
HE GAVE ME 20 BUCKS.

28:44.020 --> 28:46.989
HE SAID HE WANTED TO PULL
A PRANK ON ONE OF HIS FRIENDS.

29:09.310 --> 29:11.346
VERONICA.
THEY FOUND OUT.

29:11.380 --> 29:13.041
I DON'T KNOW HOW,

29:13.080 --> 29:15.048
BUT THEY MUST HAVE FOUND OUT
I'VE BEEN TALKING TO YOU.

29:15.080 --> 29:16.411
WHAT HAPPENED?

29:16.450 --> 29:18.782
LAST NIGHT,
THERE WAS A KNOCK ON THE DOOR,

29:18.820 --> 29:20.788
AND WHEN I OPENED IT,
I FOUND A RAT.

29:20.820 --> 29:23.015
THEY NAILED THE THING ALIVE
TO THE FRONT DOOR.

29:23.060 --> 29:24.379
PULL IT TOGETHER, RICK.

29:24.430 --> 29:26.523
WE HAVE A SEVEN-FIGURE LAWSUIT
TO WORRY ABOUT.

29:26.560 --> 29:28.448
THERE'S NO DOING THIS THING
HALFWAY.

29:28.500 --> 29:30.798
WE HAVE TO MAKE SURE
WHAT HAPPENED TO TIM

29:30.830 --> 29:32.525
NEVER HAPPENS AGAIN.

29:45.410 --> 29:49.141
YOU MISSED
OUR LAST THREE APPOINTMENTS.

29:49.180 --> 29:51.489
I'M SORRY.
I'VE BEEN BURIED.

29:51.520 --> 29:54.182
THANKS FOR WAITING AROUND
FOR ME.

29:56.960 --> 30:00.054
LILLY USED TO MAKE THIS FACE
WHEN MY MOM WAS RAILING ON ME

30:00.090 --> 30:02.320
THAT WOULD MAKE ME
LOSE IT,

30:02.360 --> 30:04.464
SO I'D TRY
NOT TO LOOK AT HER,

30:04.500 --> 30:07.833
BUT I COULD, LIKE, FEEL HER
MAKING THE FACE ON ME,

30:07.870 --> 30:10.566
AND THAT'S WHAT IT'S LIKE
ALL THE TIME.

30:10.600 --> 30:13.933
I THINK
SHE'S WATCHING ME.

30:13.980 --> 30:16.540
IT'S LIKE
WHENEVER I DO ANYTHING,

30:16.580 --> 30:19.947
I CAN FEEL HER THERE
AND SHE CAN SEE ME.

30:19.980 --> 30:22.517
IT'S LIKE
I'M NEVER, EVER ALONE.

30:24.990 --> 30:28.050
I SOUND LIKE
A TOTAL PSYCHO.

30:28.090 --> 30:30.888
YOU SOUND LIKE SOMEONE
WHO LOST A SISTER.

30:30.930 --> 30:32.454
AND HIS MIND.

30:32.490 --> 30:35.323
HOW LONG HAVE YOU BEEN
FEELING LIKE THIS?

30:35.360 --> 30:37.157
SINCE I STOPPED
TAKING MY MEDS.

30:39.030 --> 30:41.294
UH, DOES YOUR PHYSICIAN
KNOW ABOUT THIS?

30:41.340 --> 30:44.229
HAVE YOU HAD
ANY EPISODES?

30:44.270 --> 30:46.363
OH, I ONLY STOPPED
THE ANTIDEPRESSANT.

30:46.410 --> 30:48.378
I'M STILL TAKING
THE OLD STANDBYS.

30:48.410 --> 30:50.298
WHAT KIND OF EPISODES?

30:50.340 --> 30:52.376
WHAT KIND OF MEDICATION?

30:52.410 --> 30:54.446
THAT DOES EXPLAIN A LOT.

30:54.480 --> 30:56.516
THE MEDICATION
CALMED YOU --

30:56.550 --> 30:59.246
MAYBE EVEN PROHIBITED YOU

30:59.290 --> 31:01.986
FROM FULLY PROCESSING
YOUR SISTER'S DEATH.

31:02.020 --> 31:05.080
ALL THAT TURMOIL WAS SUPPRESSED
FOR THE PAST YEAR.

31:05.130 --> 31:08.156
MAYBE IT'S FINALLY MAKING
ITS WAY TO THE SURFACE.

31:10.630 --> 31:12.120
WHAT, YOU DON'T AGREE?

31:12.170 --> 31:14.934
I DON'T KNOW.

31:14.970 --> 31:17.393
I THINK SHE'S MAD
THAT I DON'T REMEMBER.

31:17.440 --> 31:19.601
ARE YOU STARTING
TO FORGET THINGS ABOUT LILLY?

31:19.640 --> 31:21.073
I REMEMBER LILLY.

31:21.110 --> 31:23.431
I JUST DON'T REMEMBER
WHAT HAPPENED.

31:23.480 --> 31:27.007
I REMEMBER BEING AT SOCCER
PRACTICE THAT MORNING...

31:27.050 --> 31:28.347
[ SIGHS ]

31:28.380 --> 31:30.644
THEN I WAS IN THE BACK
OF A LIMO,

31:30.680 --> 31:34.013
AND IT WAS THREE DAYS LATER,
AND LILLY WAS DEAD,

31:34.060 --> 31:38.929
AND ALL THAT TIME IN BETWEEN
WAS JUST...

31:38.960 --> 31:40.552
GONE.

31:40.590 --> 31:42.148
[ KNOCK ON WINDOW ]

31:42.200 --> 31:44.327
AREN'T YOU FORGETTING
SOMETHING, WALLACE?

31:44.370 --> 31:46.190
THE SECRET KNOCK?

31:47.330 --> 31:49.093
HEY! HEY!

31:51.240 --> 31:54.129
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

32:04.590 --> 32:07.081
[ SPEED DIAL BEEPING ]

32:08.690 --> 32:10.612
HEY, WALLACE.
WHATCHA DOING?

32:10.660 --> 32:12.218
UH-HUH.

32:12.260 --> 32:14.319
NO, I HAVEN'T SEEN
THAT ONE.

32:14.360 --> 32:16.499
YES, DAVE CHAPPELLE
IS GREAT.

32:16.530 --> 32:19.465
LISTEN, THE REAL REASON
I'M CALLING --

32:19.500 --> 32:21.536
FUNNY STORY.

32:34.380 --> 32:35.972
[ SIGHS ]

32:36.020 --> 32:37.647
THAN KS, WALLACE.

32:40.550 --> 32:42.188
UH, VERONICA,
I'M ASSUMING

32:42.220 --> 32:44.484
YOU DIDN'T ACCIDENTALLY
LOCK YOURSELF IN THE TRUNK.

32:44.530 --> 32:47.351
I'LL TELL YOU ABOUT IT LATER --
I HAVE TO TRACK DOWN DUNCAN

32:47.390 --> 32:49.995
AND FIGURE OUT WHERE
THE TRITONS ARE MEETING TONIGHT.

32:50.030 --> 32:52.498
Young men:
TRITON, SON OF NEPTUNE,

32:52.530 --> 32:55.738
RISE UP
FROM THE WIDE, DARK SEA.

32:55.770 --> 32:58.466
O GREAT ONE, WITH YOUR HORN,

32:58.510 --> 33:03.004
WE SUMMON YOU FROM BENEATH
THE TERRIBLE WAVES.

33:03.040 --> 33:07.409
WITH YOUR HORN,
WE SUMMON YOUR AWESOME POWERS.

33:07.450 --> 33:13.411
WITH YOUR HORN, WE SUMMON
YOUR UNRIVALED WISDOM.

33:13.450 --> 33:15.987
[ HORN BLOWS ]

33:17.720 --> 33:19.187
CONGRATULATIONS.

33:19.230 --> 33:22.051
WHEN YOU BEGAN
THIS JOURNEY 12 DAYS AGO,

33:22.100 --> 33:24.295
YOU WERE TOLD
THAT IT WOULD BE PERILOUS.

33:24.330 --> 33:26.093
I AM PLEASED TO SAY
THAT THIS YEAR,

33:26.130 --> 33:29.167
ALL THE PLEDGES HAVE PASSED
THE GREAT TRITON'S TEST.

33:29.200 --> 33:32.431
EXCEPT FOR THE KID WHO ALMOST
DRANK HIMSELF TO DEATH

33:32.470 --> 33:35.109
AND THE KID
YOU ALMOST SCARED TO DEATH.

33:35.140 --> 33:37.700
NOW THAT OUR SACRED NUMBER
IS AGAIN COMPLETE,

33:37.740 --> 33:42.313
YOU MAY LOOK UPON THE OTHER
TRITONS AS YOUR BROTHERS.

33:47.490 --> 33:49.185
HI, EVERYBODY!

33:49.220 --> 33:51.085
SAY "REPRESSED HOMOSEXUALITY"!

33:51.130 --> 33:52.722
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

33:52.760 --> 33:53.727
GOTTA BOOGIE.

33:53.760 --> 33:56.092
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

34:11.110 --> 34:13.078
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

34:22.260 --> 34:24.353
MAN! DID YOU SEE ME
LAY RUBBER?

34:24.390 --> 34:25.618
DON'T GET CARRIED AWAY.

34:25.660 --> 34:28.254
ALL I HAVE TO DO NOW
IS SHOW THAT THE TRITONS

34:28.300 --> 34:30.518
ARE THE ONES OPERATING
THE MYSTERY LOCKER --

34:30.560 --> 34:32.596
MATCH ONE OF THEIR FACES
IN THESE SHOTS

34:32.630 --> 34:36.361
WITH THE FRAME OF WHOEVER PICKED
UP THE $250 FOR YOUR FAKE I.D.

34:36.400 --> 34:38.300
PIECE OF CAKE.

34:50.850 --> 34:54.809
THIS DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.
SOMEONE HAD TO OPEN THAT LOCKER.

34:54.860 --> 34:57.158
HOW ELSE COULD
THEY HAVE GOTTEN THE MONEY?

34:57.190 --> 34:59.522
HOW ELSE COULD
THEY HAVE GOTTEN WALLACE'S NAME?

34:59.560 --> 35:02.427
VERONICA, I'M STILL HERE,
YOU KNOW?

35:02.460 --> 35:04.189
110 IS A TOP LOCKER,
RIGHT?

35:04.230 --> 35:05.197
YEP.

35:05.230 --> 35:06.424
NO ONE GOES NEAR IT.

35:06.470 --> 35:09.234
I KNOW HOW IT WENT DOWN.

35:09.270 --> 35:13.604
GREAT.
CAN I GO HOME?

35:13.640 --> 35:16.131
AARON,
THANKS FOR STOPPING BY.

35:16.180 --> 35:17.579
NO PROBLEM.

35:17.610 --> 35:20.340
I GOT TO BE AT SCHOOL AT 9:00
FOR A PARENT CONFERENCE.

35:20.380 --> 35:21.745
YOU WERE ON THE WAY.

35:21.780 --> 35:24.647
I FOUND OUT WHO'S BEEN
SELLING THE PICTURES.

35:24.690 --> 35:26.339
YOU'RE NOT GONNA LIKE IT.

35:26.390 --> 35:28.779
CAN IT GET MUCH WORSE
THAN IT ALREADY IS?

35:35.860 --> 35:38.328
YOUR COURT DATE ISN'T TILL
NEXT TUESDAY, RIGHT?

35:38.370 --> 35:40.565
WE MIGHT AS WELL CANCEL THAT
WHILE I'M HERE.

35:40.600 --> 35:43.763
REALLY?
WHY'S THAT?

35:43.800 --> 35:46.564
I THOUGHT, FOR A CHANGE,
YOU MIGHT BE INTERESTED

35:46.610 --> 35:48.828
IN HAVING THE REAL CRIMINAL
STAND TRIAL.

35:48.880 --> 35:51.474
IN THE MEANTIME, I'M GONNA HAVE
A SEAT IN YOUR LOUNGE,

35:51.510 --> 35:53.705
LEARN HOW TO TURN MEN INTO JELLY
WITH A NEW WAY OF WALKING,

35:53.750 --> 35:55.718
AND WAIT FOR THE BAD GUY
TO TURN HIMSELF IN.

35:55.750 --> 35:57.479
I DON'T HAVE TIME
FOR YOUR GAMES.

35:57.520 --> 35:59.681
AND I DON'T HAVE TIME
TO WRONGFULLY TAMPER WITH

35:59.720 --> 36:01.859
A GOVERNMENT-ISSUED DOCUMENT
IF I'M STUCK IN YOUR OFFICE.

36:01.890 --> 36:04.586
I'LL MAKE YOU
A LITTLE DEAL, LAMB.

36:04.630 --> 36:06.621
IF I DON'T DELIVER
THE PERSON

36:06.660 --> 36:09.254
WHO PUT TIM IN THE HOSPITAL
BY 5:00 PM. TODAY,

36:09.300 --> 36:11.768
I PROMISE TO WALK,
WITH A LITTLE SOMETHING EXTRA,

36:11.800 --> 36:13.597
INTO THE COURTHOUSE
ON TUESDAY

36:13.630 --> 36:16.463
AND PLEAD GUILTY TO ANYTHING
YOU WANT TO THROW AT ME.

36:16.500 --> 36:18.502
[ SIGHS ]
WHAT DO I HAVE TO DO?

36:19.910 --> 36:21.878
JUST PICK A NAME.

36:21.910 --> 36:25.471
WRITE THE NAME OF ANY STUDENT
ON THIS POST-IT,

36:25.510 --> 36:26.875
PUT IT IN THE ENVELOPE,

36:26.910 --> 36:30.346
AND HAVE ONE OF YOUR MINIONS
DROP IT INTO LOCKER 111.

36:30.380 --> 36:32.610
BY THE END OF THE DAY,
THAT KID WILL HAVE A FAKE I.D.,

36:32.650 --> 36:35.210
AND YOU'LL HAVE YOURSELF
A CROOK,

36:35.260 --> 36:38.252
AND I'LL BE SITTING OVER HERE
CHILLIN' LIKE A VILLAIN.

36:55.280 --> 36:57.271
[ DIALING ]

36:59.280 --> 37:01.919
HEY, RICK. I'M DOWN
AT THE SHERIFF'S OFFICE.

37:01.950 --> 37:05.442
HEY, THEY'RE HAULING IN
THE REAL BAD GUY THIS AFTERNOON.

37:05.490 --> 37:07.913
OH, AND I FOUND OUT
WHO THE TRITONS ARE.

37:07.950 --> 37:09.611
YOU DON'T WANT TO MISS IT.

37:09.660 --> 37:11.787
I'M GONNA NAIL THEM
TO THE WALL.

37:20.470 --> 37:22.290
SO...

37:22.340 --> 37:23.967
WHAT WAS THE PLAN?

37:24.000 --> 37:26.309
EMBARRASS ME?

37:26.340 --> 37:29.002
DESTROY MY CAREER?

37:29.040 --> 37:32.271
SOFTEN UP PUBLIC SENTIMENT FOR
A GENEROUS DIVORCE SETTLEMENT?

37:32.310 --> 37:33.641
TURN ME INTO COSTNER?

37:33.680 --> 37:35.841
OF COURSE YOU'D THINK
OF YOUR CAREER AND MONEY

37:35.880 --> 37:37.814
BEFORE YOU THINK OF
THE OBVIOUS.

37:37.850 --> 37:39.408
DID IT EVER OCCUR TO YOU,

37:39.450 --> 37:41.759
I JUST WANT TO HURT YOU
LIKE YOU'VE HURT ME?

37:41.790 --> 37:44.054
YOU HAD PRIVATE DETECT IVES
FOLLOWING ME.

37:44.090 --> 37:45.489
ONLY ON LOCATION.

37:45.530 --> 37:47.486
THE WOMEN HERE,
I'VE ALWAYS KNOWN.

37:47.530 --> 37:48.849
GOSH, MOM.
GEE, DAD.

37:48.900 --> 37:51.391
WILL I BE GOING
TO LIVE WITH GRANDMA?

37:53.070 --> 37:55.698
LISTEN TO ME --
IF YOU TRY TO DIVORCE ME,

37:55.740 --> 37:58.038
I WILL LEAVE YOU
WITH NOTHING --

37:58.070 --> 38:01.437
NO HOUSE, NO CAREER...

38:01.480 --> 38:04.574
NO CLUB MEMBERSHIPS,
NO MAID, AND NO --

38:04.610 --> 38:08.410
DAD, YOU SAY ANOTHER WORD
TO HER, AND I WILL KILL YOU.

38:10.350 --> 38:14.411
I CANNOT TAKE THIS
ANYMORE.

38:14.460 --> 38:17.349
[ SIGHS DISGUSTEDLY ]

38:46.050 --> 38:48.450
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

38:50.460 --> 38:52.587
THE THING ABOUT
A FELONY CHARGE

38:52.630 --> 38:54.689
IS IT DOESN'T GET
WIPED OFF YOUR RECORD

38:54.730 --> 38:56.550
JUST BECAUSE YOU TURN 18.

38:56.600 --> 38:58.488
IT'S LIKE THIS BLACK EYE

38:58.530 --> 39:00.623
THAT YOU HAVE
THE WHOLE REST OF YOUR LIFE.

39:00.670 --> 39:02.069
OOH!

39:05.410 --> 39:06.638
IS HE HERE YET?

39:06.670 --> 39:08.729
HE JUST ARRIVED.

39:08.780 --> 39:11.977
IT'S JUST LIKE SHE SAID --
FOUND THE FAKE IN HIS LOCKER.

39:12.010 --> 39:13.568
PROCESS OF ELIMINATION.

39:13.610 --> 39:14.838
I DIDN'T DO IT.

39:14.880 --> 39:17.110
WHAT, ME?
ARE YOU CRAZY?

39:17.150 --> 39:19.641
HOW ELSE DO YOU EXPLAIN
THE $250 IN YOUR WALLET?

39:20.850 --> 39:22.886
COUGH IT UP.

39:22.920 --> 39:25.753
BIG DEAL. THIS MONEY'S MINE.
THAT DOESN'T PROVE ANYTHING.

39:25.790 --> 39:28.395
WHY DON'T YOU TAKE A CLOSER LOOK
AT THE ONE ON TOP.

39:28.430 --> 39:30.421
READ WHAT'S WRITTEN
OVER GRANT'S HEAD.

39:30.460 --> 39:33.861
"VERONICA MARS IS...
SMARTER THAN ME."

39:33.900 --> 39:35.561
OH, YOU, STOP IT!

39:35.600 --> 39:38.660
THIS IS RICK'S LOCKER DEPUTY
SACKS PUT THE ENVELOPE IN?

39:38.710 --> 39:40.132
NOT EXACTLY.

39:57.790 --> 40:00.429
THE NIGHT TIM WENT
TO THE HOSPITAL, HE AND RICK

40:00.460 --> 40:03.497
WERE USING THEIR OWN FAKE I.D.s,
BUYING THEIR OWN DRINKS,

40:03.530 --> 40:06.169
AND ENJOYING THE PROFITS
OF THEIR OWN FAKE-I.D. BIZ.

40:06.200 --> 40:07.519
YOU WERE NEVER HAZED.

40:07.570 --> 40:08.992
YOU TRIED BLAMING
THE TRITONS

40:09.040 --> 40:10.962
BECAUSE YOU WERE
PISSED OFF AT THEM.

40:11.000 --> 40:12.934
YOUR DAD AND YOUR BROTHER
ARE TRITONS,

40:12.970 --> 40:14.972
BUT YOU DIDN'T MEASURE UP,
DID YOU, RICK?

40:15.010 --> 40:18.446
YOU WEREN'T EVEN INVITED
TO JOIN THEIR SECRET SOCIETY.

40:18.480 --> 40:20.903
SO WHEN YOU WERE CALLED
INTO THE OFFICE,

40:20.950 --> 40:24.909
YOU DUMPED A BUNCH OF
BLANK I.D.s AND YOU BLAMED ME.

40:24.950 --> 40:26.542
BUT WHY ME?

40:26.590 --> 40:29.479
WAS IT JUST BECAUSE
PEOPLE WOULD BELIEVE I DID IT?

40:30.990 --> 40:32.855
ALL RIGHT.

40:32.890 --> 40:34.926
SINCE YOU ASKED.

40:34.960 --> 40:37.099
LAST YEAR,
YOUR DAD WAS HIRED

40:37.130 --> 40:40.099
TO TRACK DOWN A HEDGE-FUND
MANAGER FOR EMBEZZLEMENT.

40:40.130 --> 40:41.768
THAT WAS MY FATHER.

40:41.800 --> 40:44.530
ONLY, THE NEWSPAPERS
NEVER MENTIONED THAT HIS COMPANY

40:44.570 --> 40:47.459
CHEATED HIM OUT OF HIS BONUS
THREE YEARS RUNNING.

40:47.510 --> 40:50.070
THEY TOOK OUR HOUSE.
THEY TOOK OUR CARS.

40:50.110 --> 40:52.704
EVENTUALLY,
MY PARENTS GOT A DIVORCE.

40:55.050 --> 40:56.745
YOU MUST BE PROUD.

41:03.560 --> 41:05.084
HEY.

41:06.830 --> 41:08.183
THESE ARE FOR YOU.

41:08.230 --> 41:11.051
YOU LOOK KIND OF CUTE
IN ONE OF THEM --

41:11.100 --> 41:13.159
SURPRISED, BUT CUTE.

41:13.200 --> 41:15.065
[ CHUCKLES ]

41:15.100 --> 41:17.068
YOUR SECRET'S SAFE
WITH ME.

41:19.110 --> 41:21.237
I HEARD THAT GUY TIM
CAME OUT OF HIS COMA.

41:21.270 --> 41:23.773
YEAH.

41:25.750 --> 41:28.548
LOOK, I NEVER SHOULD HAVE
DOUBTED YOU, DUNCAN.

41:28.580 --> 41:30.775
I'M SORRY I CAME AFTER
THE TRITONS.

41:30.820 --> 41:33.186
AND WHO ARE THE TRITONS?

41:33.220 --> 41:34.619
[ CHUCKLES ]

41:39.190 --> 41:41.055
ANOTHER HOLE
IN DUNCAN'S MEMORY.

41:41.090 --> 41:42.751
AT LEAST HE CAN JOKE ABOUT IT.

41:42.800 --> 41:44.199
TO PASS HIM IN THE HALLWAY,

41:44.230 --> 41:46.619
YOU'D NEVER GUESS
THAT ANYTHING WAS WRONG,

41:46.670 --> 41:48.797
BUT I HEARD IT
OUT OF HIS OWN MOUTH.

41:48.840 --> 41:52.298
SO, WHAT EXACTLY IS
YOUR MYSTERY ILLNESS, DUNCAN,

41:52.340 --> 41:54.672
AND WHAT OTHER PILLS
ARE YOU TAKING?

41:54.710 --> 41:57.679
* AND I FEEL SO AFRAID

41:57.710 --> 42:00.201
* AND I FEEL ALL RIGHT

42:00.250 --> 42:02.912
Man on police radio:
DISPATCH, THIS IS KING 12

42:02.950 --> 42:05.214
REQUESTING ASSISTANCE
FOR A POSSIBLE JUMPER

42:05.250 --> 42:06.945
ON THE CORONADO BRIDGE.

42:06.990 --> 42:09.709
